  "body": "# Armor Damage Indicator\n\nA simple, flat armor damage indicator like tactical games\n\n## Color schemes\n<div align=\"center\">\n    <img src=\"https://github.com/CaioFTNT/Armor-Damage-Indicator/raw/main/assets/GYR.png?raw=true\" alt=\"green-yellow-red\" height=\"150\">\n    <img src=\"https://github.com/CaioFTNT/Armor-Damage-Indicator/raw/main/assets/WR.png?raw=true\" alt=\"white-red\" height=\"150\">\n    <img src=\"https://github.com/CaioFTNT/Armor-Damage-Indicator/raw/main/assets/TR.png?raw=true\" alt=\"transparent-red\" height=\"150\">\n</div>\n\n## Features\n- Displays current armor durability on the HUD\n- Multiple color schemes (Green-Yellow-Red, Green-Red, White-Red, Transparent-Red)\n- Minimal and flat style, inspired by tactical games like PZ and Escape from Tarkov\n- Configurable positioning, size and opacity\n\n## Screenshots\n<div align=\"center\">\n    <img src=\"https://github.com/CaioFTNT/Armor-Damage-Indicator/raw/main/assets/Screenshot1.png?raw=true\" alt=\"ss1\">\n</div>\n<div align=\"center\">\n    <img src=\"https://github.com/CaioFTNT/Armor-Damage-Indicator/raw/main/assets/Screenshot2.png?raw=true\" alt=\"ss2\">\n</div>\n<div align=\"center\">\n    <img src=\"https://github.com/CaioFTNT/Armor-Damage-Indicator/raw/main/assets/Screenshot3.png?raw=true\" alt=\"ss3\">\n</div>",
